Tub Ceev Xwm Viagra


Production Year:

2010

Producer(s):

Tsia Cha

Writer(s):

Mykurt Lor

Publisher:

EU Entertainment

Release Type:

DVD

Zaj movie no yog ua txog ib lus zos hmoob nyob rau hauv thaib teb, ua tau muaj ob tug hmoob asmeskas tau los tuag, thiaj muaj ib tus tub ceev xwm tuaj mus tshawb nrhiav seb ob tug hmoob asmeskas no yog ua cas thiaj tuag. Nyob rau lub zos ntawv kuj muaj ob tug tub ceev xwm ua xaim oob qhab nyob hauv thiab. thiaj li muaj kev sib ntaus sib tua, lom sem thiab txaus luag kawg li.
